{"tid":1550384,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"再咁落去全世界一齊炒車","createTime":"2019-09-07T15:49:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T16:21:08.000Z","uid":254843,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7450bf5437cc0774a8072591e413311237b95232","tid":1550384,"uid":254843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:49:14.000Z","msg":"唔信？而家反送中傳fake news外國人都知 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要係呢排大家主力嘅twitter<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/qmoqSt7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqmoqSt7.jpg&h=da1b7c2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><br />\n多謝 雄獅巴打 翻譯 </span><strong><br />\n「我見到#antiELAB #Hong KongProtests 有好多假新聞流傳。可能係因為示威者同警察已經無信任可言，又或者因為示威持續幾個月後，示威者需要搏一搏令民憤可以持續。」<br />\n「發生咗嘅事其實夠晒離譜。講真，你地真係唔洗再作故仔，或者相信一啲無實則證據嘅故仔。唔好習慣發生咗嘅事。應該為之而憤怒。堅持討回公道。」</strong><br />\n<br />\n呢篇文除左講出最近fake news橫行情況，仲提左兩點好值得大家參考下<br />\n1. <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">點樣Spin呢排大家傳fake news</span></strong>：集中講返黑警點樣混入人群，警權過大等等又過份又有畫面嘅資料，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">講出黑警已經不值得信任，因而引起公眾不安 </span></strong><br />\n2. <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">文宣點行落去</span></strong>：搵已經有實證嘅事，集中煲大佢，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">運動過左幾個月，要再搵方向，但一定唔係fake news </span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n搞到傳媒同外國人炒車，之後愈來愈少國際關注<br />\n搞到自己友炒車，大家都愈來愈疲乏，心理壓力極大 <br />\n運動變成單一化，唔洗講證據，冇畫面冇新行動 <br />\n<strong>求下大家，一齊諗下新方法，冇得FC冇FC嘅消息盡量少傳</strong>"},{"pid":"bb9e6ce3b009e7fc29b3c72cb7980356d1a4c533","tid":1550384,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:49:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"05115b6b673522fbaab1aa189bc614ca5b862a6f","tid":1550384,"uid":39239,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:55:58.000Z","msg":"強調番要爭取嘅嘢  例如香港一直都有嘅言論 集會 資金自由<br />\n如果剩講四大訴求 外國會覺得 wfc  因為港共表面上退後咗<br />\n<br />\n同埋強調警暴  連外國人都捉"},{"pid":"216ba21dd5669526fe45dae2c29ed4f8bcd948d8","tid":1550384,"uid":254843,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"05115b6b673522fbaab1aa189bc614ca5b862a6f","tid":1550384,"uid":39239,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:55:58.000Z","msg":"強調番要爭取嘅嘢  例如香港一直都有嘅言論 集會 資金自由<br />\n如果剩講四大訴求 外國會覺得 wfc  因為港共表面上退後咗<br />\n<br />\n同埋強調警暴  連外國人都捉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:00:05.000Z","msg":"無錯，其實呢幾日極多文宣核彈<br />\n大家就不停圍住冇法子求證嘅野係咁兜圈 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n四大訴求都仲可以澄清，果日林鄭出黎都有文宣做野<br />\n但太子打人到底打到幾勁，英文文宣反而相對少<br />\n來來去去都係香港人圍內自己懷疑有人出事但又冇證據 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我明有手足可能出事係好不安<br />\n但我自己都炒左幾次車，仲有一次FC到有人借刀傳仇家個名係太子出事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cae3c520bdc2662287ae6ae614cf638b01bbe319","tid":1550384,"uid":181778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:04:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4f3cc8313f96953dd3b70469e683744c214918d3","tid":1550384,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:04:51.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">所有集會開始前，應先唱頌或奏《願榮光歸香港》<br />\n<br />\n參加者應當起立，肅立致敬<br />\n右手置於心胸前<br />\n任何非宗教的頭飾應摘除並放置於左肩</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QQQpnEV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQQQpnEV.png&h=d7a5b483&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c9d9fc5982eb06606ce754598553cfd532594efc","tid":1550384,"uid":254843,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cae3c520bdc2662287ae6ae614cf638b01bbe319","tid":1550384,"uid":181778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:04:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:04:53.000Z","msg":"求下大家由fake news沉底，或者唔好再推"},{"pid":"58e6024997921c89e713c57d8c14ab13af6cdaa3","tid":1550384,"uid":191588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:05:08.000Z","msg":"推屌你"},{"pid":"795a4218079928b4ee329acdc871ba48a3e7379f","tid":1550384,"uid":202426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:18:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ab61777b048f772fe36a4e37d8ac23440c874b4","tid":1550384,"uid":202426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:18:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7024f7898a517c2560c9c6d9f749f793777d03df","tid":1550384,"uid":254843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4ab61777b048f772fe36a4e37d8ac23440c874b4","tid":1550384,"uid":202426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:18:18.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:18:38.000Z","msg":"唔該晒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e9db2ef97fa69f7ba64bbcb80817a462ca69247","tid":1550384,"uid":23079,"like":0,"